import React from 'react'
import MealsSummary from './MealsSummary'
import AvailableMeals from './AvailableMeals'
import { Fragment } from 'react'

const Meals = () => {
  return <Fragment>
      <MealsSummary/>
      <AvailableMeals/>
  </Fragment>
}

export default Meals
